NoteLiteral.En:
Entry requirements:
•	Student at any of the universities of the ECIU;
•	At least 90 ECTS completed at the undergraduate level;
•	B2 level of English language proficiency.
Documents to be submitted in English:
•	Motivation letter – personal motivation to join the challenge, attitude towards experimenting and trying out new educational models, previous experience on the challenge topic;
•	Transcript of Records – proof of enrolment in a Bachelor’s or Master’s degree programme in any of the universities of the ECIU, proving that the student has completed at least 90 ECTS at the undergraduate level, and the study field/programme; this does not apply to KTU students (if you are a KTU student, you may attach a blank page);
•	Copy of ID card/passport in „other“ – a document issued by the country of origin (needed for registration to university services); this does not apply to KTU students (if you are a KTU student, you may attach a blank page).
Please note that documents submitted not in English will not be processed further in the admission process.

MoreInformation.NoteLiteral:
**Entry requirements:**

- Student at any of the universities of the ECIU;
- At least 90 ECTS completed at the undergraduate level;
- B2 level of English language proficiency.

**Documents to be submitted in English:**

- Motivation letter – personal motivation to join the challenge, attitude towards experimenting and trying out new educational models, previous experience on the challenge topic;
- Transcript of Records – proof of enrolment in a Bachelor’s or Master’s degree programme in any of the universities of the ECIU, proving that the student has completed at least 90 ECTS at the undergraduate level, and the study field/programme; this does not apply to KTU students (if you are a KTU student, you may attach a blank page);
- Copy of ID card/passport in „other“ – a document issued by the country of origin (needed for registration to university services); this does not apply to KTU students (if you are a KTU student, you may attach a blank page).

Please note that documents submitted not in English will not be processed further in the admission process.

The admission results will be announced in 03 March, 2025. Please check your ECIU inbox, you will have 2 days to accept the offered place.
